<title>UK: P&amp;U to announce charges, cost savings in H2.</title>
<headline>P&amp;U to announce charges, cost savings in H2.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-07-29</dateline>
<text>
<p>Swedish-U.S. drugs group Pharmacia &amp; Upjohn Inc said on Tuesday it would announce charges and cost savings linked to its most recent round of restructuring in the second half of 1997.  </p>
<p>Earlier this month the group's new president and chief executive officer Fred Hassan announced a series of initiatives aimed at simplifying P&amp;U's complex international structure and its decision-making processes.</p>
<p>These included creating a single, worldwide structure for operations including sales, marketing, research and development.</p>
<p>--London Newsroom +44 171 542 7717</p>
